Perhaps dissolved in your tea to mask the bitterness.

513
00:36:45,240 --> 00:36:47,870
别回答  我现在就终止这场审判
Don't answer. I'm putting a stop to this, right now.

514
00:36:47,950 --> 00:36:49,441
法官大人 如果她服用了此药 
Your Honors, if she is on drugs, 

