517
00:36:52,870 --> 00:36:54,790
法官大人  我必须强烈反对
Your Honors, I have to strongly object.

518
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:56,580
他显然试图在掩盖一些事情
He's obviously trying to cover something up, here.

519
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:59,630
