Yes, I am.

524
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:31,410
没有问题了
No further questions.

525
00:37:32,290 --> 00:37:35,080
亚当玛先生 难道你不问我为什么吗?
Mr. Adama, aren't you going to ask me why?

526
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:39,590
什么?  我为什么又再次服用卡马拉?
I'm sorry? Why am I taking chamalla again?

527
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:42,800
这并没有很大关系
It's not strictly relevant.

528
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:46,380
也许与你没什么相干 但却和我有关系
Well, perhaps it's not relevant to you, but it's relevant to me.

529
00:37:49,260 --> 00:37:51,850
继续 问我为什么?
Go ahead. Ask me why.

530
00:37:53,810 --> 00:37:55,770
要有始有终
Finish what you started.

531
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:04,490
您为什么又再次服用卡马拉 总统阁下?
Why are you talking the chamalla again, Madam President?

532
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:13,370
我再次服用卡马拉是因为我的癌症复发了
I am taking chamalla again because my cancer has returned.

533
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:39,560
她出现幻觉这一事实 
You know, the fact that she's having hallucinations

534
00:38:39,650 --> 00:38:41,900
与为波塔尔的辩护有联系
is relevant to Baltar's defense.

535
00:38:43,070 --> 00:38:45,480
这就是法制的运作方式  小杜
That's the way the system works, Dee.

536
00:38:45,570 --> 00:38:48,820
被告有权就证人的可信度提出异议
The accused has a right to challenge the credibility of witnesses against him.

537
00:38:48,910 --> 00:38:50,030
事实就是如此
That's just the way it is.

538
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:52,160
法制已经失效了  李
The system is broken, Lee.

539
00:38:52,830 --> 00:38:54,660
法制选举了那个男人当总统 
The system elected that man to be president

540
00:38:54,740 --> 00:38:56,910
法制还要让他逍遥法外
and the system is trying to let him walk.

541
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,960
这样的制度不值得我们去捍卫
That is not a system that deserves to be defended.

542
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:02,250
应该废除  应该重建
It deserves to be taken apart and put back together again.

543
00:39:04,670 --> 00:39:06,420
我希望...
You know, I wish...

544
00:39:12,930 --> 00:39:14,560
我希望我能够让你明白
I wish I could make you understand.

545
00:39:14,640 --> 00:39:16,600
我明白  李
I do understand, Lee.

546
00:39:16,980 --> 00:39:18,770
所以我才要离开的
That's why I'm leaving.

547
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:22,190
你不明白
Well, you don't.

548
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:26,110
你他妈的不明白
You frakking don't.

549
00:39:37,870 --> 00:39:40,370
总统阁下 您对自己身患癌症所知多久了?
Madam President, how long have you known about the cancer?

550
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:41,540
大约一周的时间
About a week.

551
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:43,380
病情如何?
And how advanced is the disease?

552
00:39:43,460 --> 00:39:46,750
您还会从半赛昂人那里输血吗?
Will you be getting any more transfusions from the half-Cylon donor?

553
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:49,380
我现在不想过多谈及像这样的细节
You know, this is the kind of detail I'm not going to go into now.

554
00:39:49,470 --> 00:39:52,380
我们正在研究对策  制定好计划后我会通知你
You know, we're looking at a game plan. I'll let you know when we have one.

555
00:39:52,470 --> 00:39:55,720
治病对您作为总统来说有多少影响?
Well, how the treatment for your illness impact your duties as president?

556
00:39:55,810 --> 00:39:57,310
目前来说 一点也没有
So far, it hasn't at all.

557
00:39:57,390 --> 00:39:59,140
您当前正在服用卡马拉汁么?
Are you currently taking chamalla extract?

558
00:39:59,230 --> 00:40:00,480
别回答这个问题
Don't answer that.

559
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:03,730
您出现幻觉的间隔有多久?
How often do you hallucinate?

560
00:40:03,810 --> 00:40:05,440
好了 胡说八道够了没有
All right, enough of this crap.

561
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,860
到此为止 托莉
We're done here. Tory.

562
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:08,900
你们这些秃鹰可以去找其他死尸了
You vultures can go pick over another carcass.

563
00:40:08,990 --> 00:40:10,820
托莉 过来
Tory! Come here.

564
00:40:11,740 --> 00:40:13,660
我们里面见  谢谢
I'll see you inside. Thank you.

565
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:24,880
不好意思 最近舰队里的温度比较高
I'm sorry. Temperatures are running a little high in the fleet these days.

566
00:40:25,090 --> 00:40:26,460
到谁了?
Who's next?

567
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:27,590
克伦
Karen?

568
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:30,670
总统阁下 您还要活多久?
Madam President, how long do you have to live?

569
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:35,010
您还要活多久  克伦?
How long do you have to live, Karen?

570
00:40:46,110 --> 00:40:47,110
您处理得很好
You handled that well.

571
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:48,610
你却没做好
You didn't.

572
00:40:49,530 --> 00:40:51,780
用找其他死尸和我做对比?
"Picked over another carcass," as opposed to mine?

573
00:40:51,860 --> 00:40:54,450
这话被媒体听到可有的瞧了
That's gonna look good in the press.

574
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:56,780
我不知道为什么自己会那么说
I don't even know why I said that. I...

575
00:40:56,870 --> 00:40:58,700
你这是怎么了?
What is up with you?

576
00:40:58,790 --> 00:41:01,290
几天来 你都无法正常工作  心神不宁  疲惫不堪
You've been off your game for days. You're distracted, you're exhausted.

577
00:41:01,370 --> 00:41:04,120
坦率地讲 你简直让人讨厌
You're just, you know, frankly, you're plain obnoxious.

578
00:41:04,210 --> 00:41:06,790
我近来睡眠不好
I just haven't been sleeping very well.

579
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:10,460
你要马上调整过来  把精力放在工作上
You need to pull it together and focus on your job, fast,

580
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:12,210
否则我照样能找到 
or I can find someone

581
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:16,180
每周梳一次头发的人来应付媒体
who can handle the press, as well as pull a comb through their hair once a week

582
00:41:43,580 --> 00:41:45,750
中尉   早安  副长
Lieutenant. Good morning, XO.

583
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:48,710
早安
Good morning.

584
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:52,300
暂时代班而已 上校会…
It's just temporary. The Colonel will...

585
00:41:52,380 --> 00:41:53,460
振作起来的
Pull it together.

586
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:54,720
说得对
Right.

587
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:57,430
我们利用泰里恩船作为诱饵...
So, we're using the tylium ship as a decoy

588
00:41:57,510 --> 00:42:01,850
把赛昂人吸引到了几乎与我们方向相反的这条航线上
to lead the Cylons along this course, here, almost directly opposite to ours.

589
00:42:01,930 --> 00:42:06,140
当他们抵达这一点的时候 他们就会重新校准超光速引擎
When they reach this point here, they'll recalibrate the FTL,

590
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:07,810
开始往回跳跃
and start jumping back to rendezvous with Galactica

591
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:11,270
并将与全体舰队在爱奥尼亚星云这里相遇
and the rest of the fleet, here, at the lonian Nebula.

592
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:13,480
发现任何赛昂人追踪他们的迹象了吗?
Any indications the Cylons are following them?

593
00:42:13,570 --> 00:42:17,360
还没有 他们似乎也停止追踪我们了
Nothing yet. And it would appear they've stopped following us as well.

594
00:42:17,450 --> 00:42:19,490
自从泰里恩船脱离舰队以后 
Our trailing Raptor has yet to pick up any sign of pursuit

595
00:42:19,570 --> 00:42:22,120
我们的猛禽机没发现任何跟踪迹象
since the tylium ship left the fleet.

596
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:25,160
还有多少次跳跃 我们才能到达那座星云?
How many jumps until we reached the nebula?

597
00:42:25,250 --> 00:42:26,460
呃
Uh...

598
00:42:26,710 --> 00:42:29,500
难以置信 只需最后三次了
It's hard to believe, we're down to the last three.

599
00:42:32,090 --> 00:42:33,300
好
Good.

600
00:42:35,090 --> 00:42:37,130
还有什么事吗  长官?
Is there anything else, sir?

601
00:42:38,130 --> 00:42:39,970
没有  我只是…
No, no. I was just...

602
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:45,060
只是想起在卡布里卡上...
Just remembering back on Caprica

603
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:48,270
当要变天的时候 你就能…
when the weather was about to change. You'd...

604
00:42:48,350 --> 00:42:50,690
在空气中闻到这股味道
You'd get this smell in the air.

605
00:42:51,650 --> 00:42:54,780
这时可能是烈日当空 万里无云
I mean, the sun could be out, not a cloud in the sky,

606
00:42:54,860 --> 00:42:57,860
可你还是能闻到这股味道 并且知道…
but you'd pick up this smell and you knew that

607
00:42:58,280 --> 00:43:00,530
有什么事情要发生了
something was just over the horizon.

608
00:43:03,990 --> 00:43:08,040
要变天了  菲里克斯  我们要做好准备
Weather's changing, Felix. We need to be ready for it.

609
00:43:12,630 --> 00:43:14,420
风暴即将来临了
There's a storm coming.

610
00:43:30,350 --> 00:43:32,350
在船里
It's in the ship.

611
00:43:34,900 --> 00:43:37,690
在他娘的船里
It's in the frakking ship!

